data.description: Charming one-level home in the sought-after Columbia Heights neighborhood! This spacious residence boasts a large primary bedroom, offering ample space for relaxation and comfort. Situated in a great location, this property provides easy access to all the amenities and conveniences of city living. The highlight of this home is its expansive fenced backyard, perfect for outdoor activities and entertaining. Additionally, the walkout basement adds versatility and potential to the property. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a delightful home in Columbia Heights!
